{"word":"Tabernacles, Feast of","slug":"tabernacles,-feast-of","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tabernacles, Feast of</b> Called also Feast of Ingathering.<br/> Instituted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=16'>Exo 23:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=22'>Exo 34:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=43'>Lev 23:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=29&verse=40'>Num 29:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=16'>Deu 16:16</a><br/> Design of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=43'>Lev 23:43</a><br/> The law read in connection with, every seventh year<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=12'>Deu 31:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=18'>Neh 8:18</a><br/> Observance of:<br/> - After the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=4'>Ezr 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=18'>Neh 8:18</a> <br/> - By Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=2'>Joh 7:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=14'>Joh 7:14</a> <br/> - Omitted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=17'>Neh 8:17</a> <br/> Penalty for not observing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=19'>Zec 14:19</a><br/> Jeroboam institutes an idolatrous feast to correspond to, in the eighth month<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ki 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=11'>1Ch 27:11</a>"}]}